<p><foreign> Gloria Patri... Sicut erat...</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>PSALMOA 121.</hi></p>
<p><foreign> L&AElig;TATUS sum in his qu&aelig; dicta sunt mihi; * In domum Domini ibimus.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign> Stantes erant pedes nostri * in atriis tuis, Jerusalem.</foreign></p>
