<p><foreign> Propter domum Domini Dei nostri, * qu&aelig;sivi bona tibi.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign> Gloria Patri... Sicut erat...</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>PSALMOA 126.</hi></p>
<p><foreign> NISI Dominus &aelig;dificaverit domum, * in vanum laboraverunt qui &aelig;dificant eam.</foreign></p>
